#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""End-to-end AI-generation test: FastAPI + Flutter pizzeria ordering app.

Generates a wrapper containing ``python-fastapi-skel`` (backend) and
``flutter-skel`` (frontend) via ``skel-gen-ai`` with domain-specific
prompts that replace the generic items CRUD with a pizzeria ordering
flow.  Then exercises the full order lifecycle over real HTTP:

    menu -> positions -> order -> address -> submit -> approve/reject -> feedback

This test proves the AI generation pipeline can produce a complete
domain-specific application from instructions alone.

Usage::

    _bin/skel-test-pizzeria-orders              # full run
    _bin/skel-test-pizzeria-orders --keep       # leave wrapper on disk
    _bin/skel-test-pizzeria-orders --port 18790 # custom port
    _bin/skel-test-pizzeria-orders --no-skip    # fail on missing toolchain

Exit codes::

    0 -- every check passed
    1 -- at least one check failed
    2 -- toolchain missing or Ollama unreachable (setup skip)
"""

